class="entry-header entry-header-single"><h1 class="entry-title">
<a
href=https://www.loveandlemons.com/mashed-sweet-potatoes/ rel=bookmark>Mashed Sweet Potatoes</a></h1></header><div
class="entry-content entry-content-single"><p
class=first-sentence>No matter who you're serving, these mashed sweet potatoes are guaranteed to be a hit! They're smooth, creamy, and full of sweet and savory flavor.</p><div
class=entry-meta><div
class=lnl-tags>
<a
href=/recipes/fall-recipes/ >fall</a> / <a
href=/recipes/side-dish-recipes/ >side dishes</a> &mdash; <a
