class=under-h2></div><div
class=pin-hidden-image-container>
<img
src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0naHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmcnIHdpZHRoPScnIGhlaWdodD0nJz48L3N2Zz4=" data-pin-description data-pin-media=https://cdn.loveandlemons.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/mashed-sweet-potatoes-pin.jpg></div><p>
<span
class="pibfi_pinterest ">
<img
class="alignnone wp-image-52775 size-full" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0naHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmcnIHdpZHRoPScxMTYwJyBoZWlnaHQ9JzE2MjknPjwvc3ZnPg==" data-original=https://cdn.loveandlemons.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/mashed-sweet-potatoes-1.jpg alt="Mashed sweet potatoes" width=1160 height=1629 data-pin-description="These mashed sweet potatoes are SO creamy and delicious! Seasoned with garlic, ginger, and rosemary, they're an easy, healthy, and flavorful side dish. Perfect for the holidays! | Love and Lemons #thanksgiving #holidayrecipes #sweetpotatoes #sidedish" data-srcset="https://cdn.loveandlemons.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/mashed-sweet-potatoes-1.jpg 1160w, https://cdn.loveandlemons.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/mashed-sweet-potatoes-1-214x300.jpg 214w, https://cdn.loveandlemons.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/mashed-sweet-potatoes-1-729x1024.jpg 729w, https://cdn.loveandlemons.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/mashed-sweet-potatoes-1-71x100.jpg 71w, https://cdn.loveandlemons.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/mashed-sweet-potatoes-1-580x815.jpg 580w" sizes="(max-width: 1160px) 100vw, 1160px" data-pin-url=https://www.loveandlemons.com/mashed-sweet-potatoes/ >
<span
class=xc_pin onclick="pin_this(event, 'http://pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=https://www.loveandlemons.com/mashed-sweet-potatoes/&media=https://cdn.loveandlemons.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/mashed-sweet-potatoes-1.jpg&description=These+mashed+sweet+potatoes+are+SO+creamy+and+delicious%21+Seasoned+with+garlic%2C+ginger%2C+and+rosemary%2C+they%27re+an+easy%2C+healthy%2C+and+flavorful+side+dish.+Perfect+for+the+holidays%21+%7C+Love+and+Lemons+%23thanksgiving+%23holidayrecipes+%23sweetpotatoes+%23sidedish')">
</span>
</span></p><p>If these mashed sweet potatoes aren&#8217;t a perfect holiday side dish, I don&#8217;t know what is! They&#8217;re creamy, flavorful, and blissfully easy to make. They call for just 8 ingredients (yes, including salt and pepper), and you can even make them in advance. They&#8217;re totally gluten-free, and they can be made vegan, too. No matter who you&#8217;re serving, these mashed sweet potatoes are guaranteed to be a hit.</p><p>I got the idea to make them after developing last year&#8217;s <a
href=https://www.loveandlemons.com/sweet-potato-casserole/ >sweet potato casserole recipe</a>. Don&#8217;t get me wrong, I love its nutty crumble topping, but I was especially smitten with the gingery sweet potato filling. In fact, I liked it so much that I thought it would make a tasty side dish on its own. I amped it up with garlic and rosemary, and voila! It became the smoothest, creamiest, and most flavorful mashed sweet potatoes I&#8217;d ever tasted. If you love sweet potatoes, you have to try this recipe!</p><p>
